1.2 样式及参数¶

NetworkX

  • node_size: (300)
  • node_color: ('r''b')
  • node_shape: 'o'
  • alpha: (1.00)
  • width: (1.0)
  • edge_color: ()
  • style: ( solid|dashed|dotted,dashdot)
  • with_labels: True
  • font_size: (12)
  • font_color:

In [31]:
G = nx.Graph()                                  #G
G.add_node(1)                                   #1
G.add_edge(2,3)                                 #2-323
G.add_edge(3,2)                                 #3-22-3
G.add_edges_from([(1,2),(1,3)])                 #1-21-3
print "nodes:", G.nodes()                       # [1, 2, 3]
print "edges:", G.edges()                       #  [(2, 3)]
print "number of edges:", G.number_of_edges()   #   1

4.4 网络的度分布¶

  • (Degree Distribution)kP(k)
  • ER
  • P(k)kk

4.4.1 ER随机网络的度分布¶

In [96]:
G = nx.random_graphs.erdos_renyi_graph(10000,0.001)   
degree =  nx.degree_histogram(G) 
degree_index = range(len(degree)) 
degree_distribution = [degree_i / float(sum(degree)) for degree_i in degree]     #

plot(degree_index,degree_distribution,'b-',marker='o')
title("Degree distribution plot")
ylabel("density")
xlabel("degree")

savefig("ER_degree_histogram.png")

4.4.2 BA无标度网络的度分布¶

In [98]:
G = nx.random_graphs.barabasi_albert_graph(10000,2)                              #n=10000m=2BA
degree =  nx.degree_histogram(G) 
degree_index = range(len(degree)) 
degree_distribution = [degree_i / float(sum(degree)) for degree_i in degree]     #

loglog(degree_index,degree_distribution,'b-',marker='o')
title("Degree distribution plot")
ylabel("density")

    nodes=map(int, community_list[i])
    for j in nodes:
        membership[j]=i
